                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>In the nature of today’s business, one always wishes to know the credit worthiness of the other before engaging in any business with them. We understand the need for Banks to do company and business name searches before opening accounts for customers or at times before granting loans to these customers. Similarly, prior to processing of loans, there may arise a need to do a land search over the landed properties offered as securities. </p>
                        <button data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#due-collapse" class="text-right collapsed btn btn-lg btn-default">Read More</button>
