                            <p>All these are very important searches for Know Your Customer (KYC) satisfaction. Unfortunately, at times these searches take a long time and the process of handing the documents and awaiting their return may seem mundane and tedious. </p>
                            <p>Virtual Advocate has an established network with most credit trading organizations and government bodies, which allows it to collect and collate relevant information about a company or business in the shortest time possible. Through our system you may lodge your search in a matter of seconds and the request be forwarded to the firm for necessary action. You will receive progress updates of your search through e-mail and a short message (SMS). By utilizing this service, you shall avoid going into credit business with someone completely blind folded.</p>
                            <p> Virtual Advocate conducts thorough Due Diligence on: </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Companies and Businesses</strong><br>
                                    We verify the legal status of all legally registered organizations such as companies, sole proprietors, partnerships, trusts and the like.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Land</strong><br>
                                    We verify the existence and ownership of landed properties in different parts of the country.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
